aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb795afc6f557e3d3fe4e1f2b48dd3868b7dba4","tid":231053,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都話左 corsair 佢唔會玩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63e1f3a35daaba5608d0a6d5279b84641499635","tid":231053,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"HKEPC好多硬件友都係o個道<br />\n包括係腦場呀/米王等等<br />\n通常d代理比人唱點點點,代理唔想得失客即時聯絡+處理<br />\n好似之前好似有單樓主換隻牛搞極都有問題,好快搞大左件事<br />\nhkepc玩左幾十頁,代理好快主動搵番佢<br />\n不過 felton 真係麻麻<br />\n但唔知點解依加intel/amd 某d cpu 都會有佢代理<br />\n仲有asrock 呀 corsair 呀 klevv等等<br />\n反而舊代理altech好d,我去到即換,冇貨就等/比同級你,同埋可以補錢換,唔洗走兩轉<br />\n只不過位置較遠"},{"pid":"740526157fbaee2f22039ba4cbeed87a829219a6","tid":231053,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:49:10.000Z","msg":"BTW FELTON個肥仔同ALTECH之前o個個好似<br />\n唔知係唔係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89312997efe7f6d08e9c8fe1ac95c12984446938","tid":231053,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW FELTON個肥仔同ALTECH之前o個個好似<br />\n唔知係唔係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"6cccd65fb372f3fb763514efd63162682d539c5a","tid":231053,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都話左 corsair 佢唔會玩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個fd隻牛果d warranty label損左少少，話佢拆過隻牛唔保，點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d166ea0bd1f6e667ff8c6980a7a36e04d6f0046","t